The paper discusses the use of constraint programming for sequence mining, which involves finding patterns in data. This topic is relevant to several sub-categories in computer science, including artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data mining (cs.DM), machine learning (cs.LG), databases (cs.DB), and software engineering (cs.SE).
